        "command": "# Find which map file contains code near PC 0x08013074\npython3 -c \"\nimport os, glob\ntarget_pc = 0x08013074\nmaps = glob.glob('/home/user/claude-projects/stm32-substrate/tests/fixtures/projects/**/*.map', recursive=True)\nfor mf in maps:\n    try:\n        txt = open(mf).read()\n        # Look for the hex address near our PC\n        if '08013' in txt:\n            print(mf)\n    except: pass\n\"",
