        "command": "# Decode SP: 0x20018000 \u2014 check the FAULTING project's linker script for stack region\ngrep -E \"(_estack|_Min_Stack_Size|STACK|stack)\" \\\n  /home/user/claude-projects/stm32-substrate/tests/fixtures/projects/F-PROJ-NUCLEO-L476RG/Projects/NUCLEO-L476RG/Examples/PWR/FAULTING/STM32CubeIDE/STM32L476RGTX_FLASH.ld \\\n  /home/user/claude-projects/stm32-substrate/tests/fixtures/projects/F-PROJ-NUCLEO-L476RG/Projects/NUCLEO-L476RG/Examples/GPIO/BLINKY/STM32CubeIDE/STM32L476RGTX_FLASH.ld \\\n  /home/user/claude-projects/stm32-substrate/tests/fixtures/projects/F-PROJ-NUCLEO-L476RG/Projects/NUCLEO-L476RG/Examples/PWR/VCP-ECHO/STM32CubeIDE/STM32L476RGTX_FLASH.ld 2>/dev/null",
